item.title: Compile problem
item.dc:creator: @sexytimee sexytimee
item.description:
@sexytimee wrote:

If you have jdk 6u3 use this:

@echo off title Compiler "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_03\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java pause

If you have 6u4… use this:

@echo off title Compiler "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_04\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java pause

EDIT: right click your compiler and click ‘edit’ replace everything in there with one of these, according to which jdk you have.
